'''Babs Martin''' is a patient at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]] who was in the hospital for a colectomy.

==History==
===Central Line===
Babs needed a central line before surgery to get access. While [[Jo Wilson]] was placing one, the wire snagged. When Jo tried to force it out, she caused as posterior wall perforation and subclavian bleed, which required emergency surgery and would delay Babs' colectomy.
